summary: A face Preset of one of my characters
descriptionHtml:
This is a preset. There are two files a dd.s and nif please put them in Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen. Then when your in game type in showracemenu. Once thats done go to sculpt on the top right of your screen then import the head call Sylvia.nif then your done.
 Please note that your eyebrows may look odd just switch it out with something that works to your likings.


[b]REQUIREMENTS[/b]
Racemenu and SKSE!
